{"tid":1161902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫院阿婆差啲玩撚死我","createTime":"2019-05-19T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T13:50:35.000Z","uid":16510,"like":81,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"98525d17011b57f1ed1bb8b77e367a12cac52544","tid":1161902,"uid":16510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"本身去醫院探屋企人<br />\n臨走果時 有個阿婆離遠叫我<br />\n婆：先生，可唔可以帶我去拎藥啊？<br />\n我心諗 無咩所謂 助人為快樂之本啦<br />\n因為見佢拎住支拐杖 行動不便咁 同佢要求到<br />\n我就扶住佢去坐電梯<br />\n<br />\n一入升降機 有十個醫生左右<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />           婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />       醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個阿婆掉轉頭同啲醫生講<br />\n婆：我唔識呢個先生架<br />\n<br />\n我心諗屌鳩你 我唔撚識你都幫你 你玩鳩我 <br />\n做乜撚野<br />\n<br />\n升降機情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿婆你好野啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個阿婆繼續講<br />\n婆：佢唔識我都帶我去拎藥啊 好好人啊呢位先生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哇 真係嚇撚死比個阿婆<br />\n之後帶個阿婆去拎藥<br />\n中途同佢傾得幾開心<br />\n助人為快樂之本 係真架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427b6f059f6844bb353c5444254973ddfb83371a","tid":1161902,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"be042e0bde7cd3c603329726b064ff97ea741cab","tid":1161902,"uid":22488,"like":14,"dislike